quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,91,Remember the one who guarded her chastity. We breathed into her from Our Spirit and made her and her son a sign for all people
  21,92,"[Messengers], this community of yours is one single community and I am your Lord, so serve Me"
  21,93,"They have torn their unity apart, but they will all return to Us"
  21,94,"If anyone does good deeds and is a believer, his efforts will not be ignored: We record them for him"
  21,95,No community destroyed by Us can escape its return
  21,96,and when the peoples of Gog and Magog are let loose and swarm swiftly from every highland
  21,97,"when the True Promise draws near, the disbelievers’ eyes will stare in terror, and they will say, ‘Woe to us! We were not aware of this at all. We were wrong.’"
  21,98,"You [disbelievers] and what you worship instead of God will be fuel for Hell: that is where you will go"
  21,99,"if these [idols] had been real gods they would not have gone there- you will all stay there"
  21,100,"There the disbelievers will be groaning piteously, but the [idols] will hear nothing"
  21,101,But those for whom We have decreed Paradise will be kept far from Hell